This will recursively check all folders under "Orch1:\" and list those without any user assignments. Folders with inherited user assignments from parent folders will not be included, even if they have no direct user assignments.</dev:code>
        <dev:remarks>
          <maml:para></maml:para>
        </dev:remarks>
      </command:example>
    </command:examples>
